sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser (localStorage)
    participant Shell as shell/storage.ts
    participant Guard as isHighScoreEntry()
    participant Core as core/highscore.ts
    participant Renderer as Renderer

    Note over Browser,Renderer: loadHighScores() — happy path
    Shell->>Browser: getItem('tempest-high-scores')
    Browser-->>Shell: raw JSON string
    Shell->>Shell: JSON.parse()
    Shell->>Shell: Array.isArray() check
    Shell->>Guard: filter each entry
    Guard-->>Shell: ✅ valid entries only
    Shell-->>Core: HighScoreTable (clean)
    Core-->>Renderer: display leaderboard

    Note over Browser,Renderer: loadHighScores() — corrupt payload
    Shell->>Browser: getItem('tempest-high-scores')
    Browser-->>Shell: '[{}, {name:9, score:"x"}]'
    Shell->>Shell: JSON.parse() ✅
    Shell->>Shell: Array.isArray() ✅
    Shell->>Guard: filter({}) → ❌ dropped
    Shell->>Guard: filter({name:9}) → ❌ dropped
    Guard-->>Shell: [] (empty — nothing passed)
    Shell-->>Core: [] (safe empty table)
    Core-->>Renderer: empty leaderboard (no crash)

    Note over Browser,Renderer: saveHighScores(readonly table)
    Core->>Shell: saveHighScores(readonly HighScoreEntry[])
    Shell->>Browser: setItem('tempest-high-scores', JSON.stringify(table))
    Browser-->>Shell: ✅ (or quota error, swallowed)